7. Phased Roadmap
Phase 1 — MVP (Weeks 1–3)
• Electron + Vite + React scaffold with working menu bar icon
• iCal feed fetch and parse (no auth required)
• Urgency bucketing and panel render (Today / This Week / Later)
• electron-store for settings (Canvas iCal URL, lookahead window)
• Auto-launch via macOS login item registration
• Manual refresh button in panel footer
• Unsigned .app bundle via electron-builder
Phase 2 — Full Integration (Weeks 4–5)
• Canvas REST API with Personal Access Token stored in macOS Keychain
• Submission status badges on each assignment row
• macOS notifications with configurable lead times (24 h, 2 h, 30 min, 15 min)
• powerMonitor wake event triggering automatic background sync
• Per-course color coding and hide/show toggle
• Onboarding flow with step-by-step token setup guide
Phase 3 — Polish (Optional, Weeks 6–7)
• Vibrancy / frosted glass panel background (macOS visual effect)
• Personal manual task layer alongside Canvas items
• Menu bar icon badge count for overdue and today items
• Settings import/export for easy reinstall
• Optional: open-source release for other UW Canvas users
