8. Risks & Constraints
Risk Severity Mitigation
API token security — token gives read access to all
Canvas data.
High Store exclusively in macOS Keychain via keytar.
Never log or write to disk.
iCal sync lag — Canvas iCal feed can lag 15–30 min
after an instructor edits an assignment.
Medium Document the limitation. Upgrade to REST API in
Phase 2 for near-real-time data.
Canvas API rate limiting — excessive polling could
trigger HTTP 429 responses.
Medium Default sync interval of 30 min. Implement
exponential backoff on 429. Cache aggressively.
macOS Gatekeeper — unsigned .app bundles trigger
a security warning on first open.
Low For personal use: right-click > Open bypasses
Gatekeeper. Document this in the README.
Electron binary size — ~150 MB installed due to
bundled Chromium.
Low Acceptable for personal use. Note for any future
public distribution.
