9. Success Metrics
For a personal utility, success is primarily qualitative — but these targets give concrete signals that the app is
working as intended.
Metric Target
Assignments missed per
quarter
0
Time to see full deadline list on
wake
< 5 seconds
Maximum sync lag from
Canvas
30 minutes (iCal) / 5 minutes (REST)
Memory footprint at steady
state
< 120 MB RAM
CPU usage between sync
cycles
< 1%
Onboarding completion time < 60 seconds from first launch
Qualitative Bar
The real signal You stop reflexively opening Canvas 'just to check.' The app becomes ambient
infrastructure — like a clock on your wall. You notice when it's missing, not when it's
working.
